steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on S Euclid Ave toward E Pleasant Dr
S Euclid Ave turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr
Turn left onto S Pierre St

Take the 1st right onto US-83 S/W Sioux Ave
Continue to follow US-83 S
Turn left to merge onto I-90 E

Take exit 396A to merge onto I-29 S toward Sioux City
Entering Iowa
Keep left to stay on I-29 S
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-29 S

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-29 S, follow signs for Kansas City
Entering Missouri
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-435 E, follow signs for Interstate 435 E/St Louis
Take exit 63B on the left for I-70 E toward Sports Complex/St Louis
Keep left, follow signs for Interstate 70 E/St Louis and merge onto I-70 E
Take the exit toward I-70 E

Keep left to continue toward I-70 E
Entering Illinois
Continue onto I-70 E
Take exit 3 to merge onto I-64 E toward Louisville
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-57 S, follow signs for Interstate 57 S/Memphis
Take exit 44 for I-24 E toward Nashville

Continue onto I-24 E
Passing through Kentucky
Entering Tennessee
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-24 E, follow signs for Interstate 24/Interstate 40 E/Chattanooga/Knoxville

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-40 E, follow signs for Interstate 40 E/Knoxville
Entering North Carolina
Keep right at the fork to continue on US-74 E, follow signs for I-26 E/Hendersonville/Spartanburg
Merge onto I-26 E/US-74 E

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-26 E
Entering South Carolina
Keep left at the fork to continue on US-76 E
Continue onto I-126 E/US-76 E
Slight left onto US-76 E (signs for Elmwood Ave/I-126)
Turn right onto Assembly St
Turn left onto Gervais St
